                <h1>Enhance Learning with Background Knowledge Activities</h1>
                <p>Background knowledge activities are essential tools for enhancing comprehension and engagement in learning environments. These activities aim to activate prior knowledge, encouraging students to make connections with new information. Engaging methods include brainstorming, concept mapping, and discussion prompts that enrich understanding and retention.</p>
